      <title>尹永哲弹劾案扩大东亚裂痕</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/opinion/articles/2024-12-16/yoon-suk-yeol-s-impeachment-widens-east-asia-fault-lines</link>
      <description><![CDATA[尹锡烈在首尔的动乱、东京几十年来最弱的政府以及唐纳德·特朗普在华盛顿重返权力舞台，意味着短暂的协调时刻即将在最糟糕的时刻结束。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/opinion/articles/2024-12-16/yoon-suk-yeol-s-impeachment-widens-east-asia-fault-lines</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 16 Dec 2024 22:00:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>吸引投资者投资美国财政部的债务风险如今已迫在眉睫</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/features/2024-12-16/trump-treasury-nominee-scott-bessent-focuses-on-us-deficit-debt-spending</link>
      <description><![CDATA[特朗普选择管理美国政府财政，是索罗斯团队的一部分，该团队导致英镑暴跌。他的新现实比任何汇率赌注都更为复杂。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/features/2024-12-16/trump-treasury-nominee-scott-bessent-focuses-on-us-deficit-debt-spending</guid>
