      <pubDate>Mon, 16 Dec 2024 21:37:48 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特鲁多任命勒布朗为加拿大财政部长 政府陷入混乱</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-16/trudeau-to-name-leblanc-canada-finance-minister-with-government-in-chaos</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加拿大总理贾斯汀·特鲁多任命多米尼克·勒布朗为加拿大财政部长，接替克里斯蒂亚·弗里兰。弗里兰的辞职信措辞严厉，令人震惊，信中暗示政府对唐纳德·特朗普回归的准备工作做得不周。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-16/trudeau-to-name-leblanc-canada-finance-minister-with-government-in-chaos</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 16 Dec 2024 20:29:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>墨西哥政府采取措施扩大住房管理部门权力</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-16/mexico-government-moves-to-expand-its-powers-in-housing-agency</link>
      <description><![CDATA[墨西哥总统克劳迪娅·希因鲍姆支持一项改革监管政府支持的抵押贷款机构 Infonavit 的法律的提议，该提议将大大扩展该公司的权限，取消一系列制衡机制，从而使她的政府完全拥有决策权。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-16/mexico-government-moves-to-expand-its-powers-in-housing-agency</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 16 Dec 2024 19:43:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普称泽连斯基应准备达成协议以结束战争</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-16/trump-says-zelenskiy-should-prepare-to-make-deal-to-end-war</link>
      <description><![CDATA[当选总统唐纳德·特朗普表示乌克兰需要达成协议以结束俄罗斯的入侵，并淡化了被占土地的价值，这是他可能推动将俄罗斯领土收益纳入法律的解决方案的最新信号。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-16/trump-says-zelenskiy-should-prepare-to-make-deal-to-end-war</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 16 Dec 2024 18:41:46 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普谴责无人机“悬念” 白宫称无风险</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-16/trump-says-us-military-keeping-public-in-suspense-on-drones</link>
      <description><![CDATA[当选总统唐纳德·特朗普暗示美国政府让美国人对这些无人机目击事件“心存疑虑”，白宫表示，执法部门对新泽西州和其他东北部各州报告的数千起无人机目击事件进行了评估，认为没有必要感到恐慌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-16/trump-says-us-military-keeping-public-in-suspense-on-drones</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 16 Dec 2024 17:30:57 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>内塔尼亚胡在军事胜利后再次试图增强权力</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-16/netanyahu-tries-again-to-boost-his-power-after-military-wins</link>
      <description><![CDATA[每天都有人威胁要解雇司法部长。因为首席大法官是自由派而取消其原定的任命。更换政府部门的法律监督员。以更有可能影响阿拉伯人的方式限制谁可以竞选公职。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-16/netanyahu-tries-again-to-boost-his-power-after-military-wins</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 16 Dec 2024 13:36:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
